FY_Pool_Day_v2 - v1 base by Squall :) 
-------------------------------
- One of the best CS maps (IMO) gets a remake. Thanks Squall for making it.
- The UMP and the SG550 were added.
- Don`t forget: Don`t pee in the pool! :D


------------------------

the v2 changelog :
- fixed lighting 
- ladder are added , so a new buyzone/bombzone is added 
- the glasses in spawns are breakable , and there is a passage 
- the central pool is deeper than v1 

V2 made by Lexluckyluke (france) :D 
please comment and rating , repport me for any errors ;) 

thanks <3
